 502        #region HeadContentchange
 503        private void HeadContent(XmlNodeList DocContent,string HeadInfo,string Libinfo)
 504        {
 505            string OrgCont = DocContent[0].InnerText;
 506            //Modifiying the heading content.
 507            if (HeadInfo != null)
 508            {
 509                string[] HValue = HeadInfo.TrimEnd('|').Split('|');
 510                for (int i = 0; i <= HValue.Length - 1; i++)
 511                {
 512                    string[] ValueSplit = HValue[i].Split(',');
 513                    if (ValueSplit[1].ToString() != ValueSplit[2].ToString())
 514                    {
 515                            string SearchText = ValueSplit[1].ToString() + "#" + ValueSplit[0].ToString();
 516                            string ReplaceText = ValueSplit[2].ToString() + "#" + ValueSplit[0].ToString();
 517                            OrgCont = OrgCont.Replace(SearchText, ReplaceText);
 518                    }
 519                }
 520            }
 521            //Modifiying the Library object content
 522            if (Libinfo != null)
 523            {
 524                string[] LValue = Libinfo.TrimEnd('|').Split('|');
 525                for (int j = 0; j <= LValue.Length - 1; j++)
 526                {
 527                    string[] LValueSplit = LValue[j].Split(',');
 528                    if (LValueSplit[1].ToString() != LValueSplit[2].ToString())
 529                    {
 530                        string SearchText1 = LValueSplit[1] + "#AnnotateControl.axd?";
 531                        string SearchText2 = "AttachmentID=" + LValueSplit[1];
 532                        string ReplaceText1 = LValueSplit[2].ToString() + "#" + "AnnotateControl.axd?";
 533                        string ReplaceText2 = "AttachmentID=" + LValueSplit[2].ToString();
 534                        OrgCont = OrgCont.Replace(SearchText1, ReplaceText1);
 535                        OrgCont = OrgCont.Replace(SearchText2, ReplaceText2);
 536                    }
 537                }
 538            }
 539            DocContent[0].InnerText = OrgCont;

 545        private void CheckHeading(XmlNodeList Heading,out string HStatusError,out string strErrormsg)
 546        {
 547            string AssoHIM = "AssociatedHIM";
 548            string HeadInfo = string.Empty;

 564                    //If lnResult = 0->Heading is present in target system,lnresult = 1 -> New heading has to create.

 566

 569                    string XmlAssValue = string.Empty;
 570                    if (StrAssoHIM != null && StrAssoHIM.Length > 0)
 571                    {

 584                                return;

 592                    if (HStatusError != "E")
 593                    {
 594                        if (lnresult == 1)
 595                        {

 597                            XmlNode XmlDefCitTabHIMNAME = xmlcnode.SelectSingleNode("DefaultCiTab/DefaultCiTabName");

 608                        objSerTx.ReplaceObject(objHeadInfo.HeadingOldOid, NewXml);
 609                        ImpError.Errorcollection += "<br/><font color=" + "blue" + ">" + "New Heading is replaced succes

 769        #region Collect Associated HIMAttributes
 770        private string CollectAssHIMAtt(XmlNode AssoHIM)
 771        {
 772            string StrRet = null;
 773            string HimDetTag = "HIMDetails";
 774            string HimOIDTag = "HIMOID";
 775            string HimNameTag = "HIMName";
 776
 777                for (int j = 0; j <= AssoHIM.ChildNodes.Count - 1; j++)
 778                {
 779                    XmlNode HimDetNode = AssoHIM.ChildNodes[j];
 780                    for (int k = 0; k <= HimDetNode.ChildNodes.Count - 1; k++)
 781                    {
 782                        XmlNode HimDetChildNode = HimDetNode.ChildNodes[k];
 783                        if (HimDetChildNode.Name.Contains(HimOIDTag))
 784                        {
 785                            StrRet += HimDetChildNode.InnerText + ",";
 786                        }
 787                        else if (HimDetChildNode.Name.Contains(HimNameTag))
 788                        {
 789                            StrRet += HimDetChildNode.InnerText + "|";
 790                        }
 791                    }
 792                }
 793                if (StrRet != null)
 794                {
 795                    return StrRet.TrimEnd('|');
 796                }
 797                else
 798                {
 799                    return StrRet;
 800                }

 1952        //CDC form Checking
 1953        private long FnCheckCDC(XmlNodeList CDClist,XmlNodeList Doccont)
 1954        {
 1955            long lnresult = 0;
 1956            if (CDClist == null)
 1957            {
 1958                return lnresult;
 1959            }
 1960            for (int count = 0; count <= CDClist.Count - 1; count++)
 1961            {
 1962                XmlNode CDCChild = CDClist[count];
 1963                if (CDCChild.ChildNodes.Count == 0)
 1964                    break;
 1965                string CDCCode = CDCChild["CDCFormCode"].InnerText.ToString();
 1966                string CDCFormName = CDCChild["CDCFormName"].InnerText.ToString();
 1967                string COFormID = CDCChild["CDCFormOID"].InnerText.ToString();
 1968                string COFormVersion = CDCChild["CDCFormversion"].InnerText.ToString();
 1969
 1970                string CNFormID = null;
 1971                string CNFormVersion = null;
 1972                if ((CDCCode != null) && (CDCCode != ""))
 1973                {
 1974                    GetLatestCDCInfo(CDCCode, out CNFormID, out CNFormVersion);
 1975                    if ((CNFormID == null) || (CNFormID == "") || (CNFormVersion == null) || (CNFormVersion == ""))
 1976                    {
 1977                        //No CDC Found.Throw Error
 1978                        ImpError.Errorcollection += "<br/><font color=" + "red" + ">"+"CDC Form:" + CDCCode + " is not f
 1979//                        lstError.Items.Add(LstHIMAtt);
 1980                        lnresult = 1;
 1981                    }
 1982                    else
 1983                    {
 1984                        string SText = COFormID+"*"+CDCFormName+"*"+COFormVersion;
